code: @Test public void testArchiveJob() throws Exception {     final Path tmpPath = new Path(tmpFolder.getRoot().getAbsolutePath()).     final JobID jobId = new JobID().     final Collection<ArchivedJson> toArchive = new ArrayList<>(2).     toArchive.add(new ArchivedJson("dir1", "hello")).     toArchive.add(new ArchivedJson("dir1/dir11", "world")).     final Path archive = FsJobArchivist.archiveJob(tmpPath, jobId, toArchive).     final Collection<ArchivedJson> restored = FsJobArchivist.getArchivedJsons(archive).     Assert.assertThat(restored, containsInAnyOrder(toArchive.toArray())). }
